	h2 Porvoo - The Old Medieval Town
	.story We took a coach out of Helsinki city to Porvoo, one of the six Medieval towns of Finland, just an hour away from city centre. It was as if we had time travelled. They have the famous red shore houses that created a unique backdrop for the Porvoo river - Porvoonjoki.  
