	h2 Old Porvoo Walk
	.story We took a walk along their heritage trail with the map we had gotten from the tourist's centre. Walking along the trail feels like walking in a fairy tale scene. We passed by their Town Hall and Porvoo Cathedral. Every house along the street varies from 2 to 3 storeys with hip roofs and they are donned in different pastel colours - green, yellow, red, blue, pink... you name it, they have it. That was colouring book brought to life! 
