	h2 Runeburg
	.story Porvoo is famous also because it is the home of Johan Ludwig Runeburg - Finland National Poet. They even have a tart named after him - Runeburg Tart. We went to Cabriole Restaurant that served buffet for our lunch. We had the sweet Runeburg Tart there as well. The texture of the tart is similar to a financier with strawberry jam in it. Elvin also surprised me with their famous macarons although I know he doesn't like sweet stuff - That's sweet. 
