	.story It was not a long walk but we were feeling rather tired, probably because we were not used to the little slopes around and the icy pavement. However, we were glad that we completed it. We walked back to the bus terminal and took a bus back to Helsinki. I was worried for a moment because the route back seemed longer and different from the one in the morning. It turned out that there were a couple of buses that terminate at Kamppi Bus Station. Phew, so sit back and enjoy the ride!
